  "3024560": {
    "name": "Dungeon Master",
    "steam_appid": 3024560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/1db465a1576d6bee1a1202940d3f9969.avif?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=137 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被困在一个充满危险和怪物的神秘地牢中，三名幸存者将面对无情的地牢主，在这场考验智慧与反应的残酷游戏中一决高下。选择你的阵营，踏入一个充满恐慌与追逐的跨平台非对称多人地牢爬行世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸存者以第三人称视角游玩，拥有更好的环境感知和众多可操控角色；而地牢主则在地牢上空飞行，专注于猎捕他们的猎物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次遭遇中，幸存者的目标是逃离地牢，避免被陷阱抓住或被地牢主的仆从杀死——这需要极高的技巧，尤其是地牢每次都会变化。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>核心特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/771a40d30dbe3ea75cd5b5ef4cf90505.webp?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸存者可以选择合作或独自行动。你的生存机会将取决于你是与队友协作制定策略击败地牢主，还是孤军奋战。你能否智胜地牢主，逃离他的魔爪？<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/8a608d4a4200230562fc523a1a5288cd.poster.avif?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/8a608d4a4200230562fc523a1a5288cd.webm?t=1756682945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/5a7238f32b29adde3039131222b40296.webp?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局比赛均为程序生成，你永远无法预测，也不会遇到完全相同的地牢。布局、房间、内容和宝藏都随机且不可预测。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/bcf7c88c51f78f7e129f35c3ef9b2c23.webp?t=1756682945\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/bcf7c88c51f78f7e129f35c3ef9b2c23.poster.avif?t=1756682945\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=342 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/f19c848a970d0c2b5841f8898e817d5f.webp?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位地牢主和幸存者都有自己的深度成长系统和大量可解锁内容，可以根据个人策略自由定制。经验、技能和对环境的理解是杀死幸存者或智胜地牢主的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/ac8252354694b825d00c6fea9e059aa3.webp?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=47 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为地牢主，你可以选择并定制你的陷阱和仆从。熟悉地牢房间的模式，根据经验做出明智选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/31ff92779385a3439b8899ed66f56bd6.webp?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/1454e01adb29b9c807266079258111f0.poster.avif?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/1454e01adb29b9c807266079258111f0.webm?t=1756682945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/f37f4382d932265794b024b077ecad10.webp?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=43 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/9f41658e662334f909898dfe4e32e74c.poster.avif?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/9f41658e662334f909898dfe4e32e74c.webm?t=1756682945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/0171d05385c6752536676bed4a8ebf20.webp?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=44 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索充满神话危险和陷阱的地牢。穿行于狭窄走廊、闹鬼的房间和遗忘的墓地，寻找珍贵武器、法术和技能，利用闪避能力避开、欺骗并摧毁地牢主布置的陷阱。程序生成的地牢让你永远无法预测结局。配合氛围浓厚的视觉效果、阴森的音效和动态光影，每一次冒险都紧张而恐怖。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/f96a87b2bb36abee9ca8d162f772ea8c.poster.avif?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/f96a87b2bb36abee9ca8d162f772ea8c.webm?t=1756682945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/2bf96994201fa0ad6a5b5a38fc6d552c.webp?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在地牢房间中寻找资源和古老技艺，发掘遗忘的知识。使用或分享你新获得的武器、法术、技能和装备，冲破地牢最终关卡，与地牢主展开决战——战斗决定最终的胜者。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/7df11a0956eddd27b1563a74e2a072f0.poster.avif?t=1756682945\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3024560/extras/7df11a0956eddd27b1563a74e2a072f0.webm?t=1756682945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
